::Aerotaur::
    He follows Windlord and Perplex into the chamber with Nightlight, 
Trinity, and Angel Prime.  "Hello Angel Prime.  It's good to see you again."  
He stretches a bit and reaches up to touch the back of his head.  It was 
still a little tender and he winced at the touch.  "See Trinity no little 
shot to the head is going to keep me down for long."  He grins down at her 
warmly.
